Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.53,0:16:23.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.71,0:16:24.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你
