Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:58.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,热气腾腾的味增汤和便当搭配也非常合适
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:01.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃 会长简直是天才
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.40,0:20:03.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈 别这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:05.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样啊 四宫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:07.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你不懂冷饭的美味
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.65,0:20:07.61,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是跟别人学的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.79,0:20:11.10,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,而是凭借经验的发现和灵感创造出来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:14.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:16.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜同学一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:18.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可以一起过夜真开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:22.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不疼 但是还是想哭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了藤原同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:28.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,绝交吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:32.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,轻蔑的程度上升了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:34.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 你这样出招的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:39.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要考虑反击了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:42.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,期待明天的到来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.28,0:20:50.60,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的便当真是费尽心血啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:54.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,厨师们好像都来了兴致
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.36,0:20:57.50,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.94,0:21:01.09,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 那就快来求我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:02.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,快说让我分你一口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.48,0:21:06.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我就以宽大的胸怀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:08.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,给我 给我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.05,0:21:12.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 那就和会长的便当交换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:13.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样 接受乞求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:16.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧 随时欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:19.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们也吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:20.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:25.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 今天也有好多香肠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:27.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,已经成为固定菜单了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.76,0:21:31.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很好啊 又可爱又好吃 真是最棒配菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.71,0:21:33.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,说最棒是不是有点过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:37.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么不好嘛 我就是这么认为的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.34,0:21:40.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 我知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:41.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:44.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得你喜欢吃牡蛎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:48.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,从昨天开始延续到现在的这种不安的气场到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.93,0:21:52.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么没来由的给我送高级食材
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:54.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一定在盘算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:55.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不然怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.19,0:21:59.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可爱的便当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:03.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就给可怜的会长一点施舍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:05.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在可怜我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.52,0:22:07.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,太屈辱了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:10.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不能收下 我绝对不能收下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.66,0:22:13.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你给我那么高级的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.51,0:22:14.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没什么可回礼的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:16.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,章鱼香肠就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:17.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.43,0:22:19.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,疼不疼 脑袋没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:22.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 怎么听起来都像是坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.52,0:22:26.26,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.67,0:22:30.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗 会长也帮忙做了我的份
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.44,0:22:33.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,做一人份还是两人份都没什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:36.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.30,0:22:38.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.06,0:22:42.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,便当的配色也很重要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.39,0:22:42.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:44.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,人形家畜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.51,0:22:47.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无尊严只擅长依靠他人的寄生虫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:49.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,营养都去胸上的无脑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.13,0:22:51.92,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这是何等厚脸皮的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:54.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会原谅你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:57.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宫的眼神像是暗杀者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.57,0:23:00.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 今天社团联盟要集合
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.65,0:23:01.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要赶快吃完饭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.99,0:23:05.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我的章鱼香肠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:07.07,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.04,0:23:14.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.53,0:23:16.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,像个傻子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.78,0:23:20.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.46,0:23:23.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,张开嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.93,0:23:30.01,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.95,0:23:31.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.61,0:23:44.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原同学对不起 我误会你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:46.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你毫无疑问是个人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:48.88,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前觉得我是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.60,0:23:50.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出自信来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.13,0:23:54.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都充满自信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:52.30,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,今日战局
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.12,0:23:56.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.64,0:24:03.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.53,0:24:06.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,会长真让人头疼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.32,0:24:11.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我午餐都准备成了那样还是不来告白
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.33,0:24:13.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辉夜大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:17.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,假设辉夜大小姐找到了真正的爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.04,0:24:20.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也会像现在一样等待被告白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.75,0:24:22.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,还是自己主动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:24.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,恋爱头脑战
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:28.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这是堵上双方尊严的灵魂的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.69,0:24:30.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真到了这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.26,0:24:32.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑到别人抢走的风险
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.49,0:24:34.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,合理的结论只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.94,0:24:36.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是主动告白
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.67,0:24:38.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.20,0:24:40.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.70,0:24:42.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是决定…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.70,0:24:43.48,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.95,0:24:46.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不是因为告白太丢脸了做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.88,0:24:50.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果被拒绝了该怎么办之类的无聊的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.36,0:24:51.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,才不告白的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.60,0:24:52.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,希望诸位理解
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.77,0:24:58.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事怎么样都行吧 这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.70,0:25:12.90,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君と私　きっと今同じ気持ちだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.70,0:25:12.90,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}你和我 现在一定怀着同样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.64,0:25:29.97,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君から笑いかけてくれたなら　天使でいられるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.64,0:25:29.97,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}只要有你的微笑 我就还能如天使一般
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.49,0:25:35.99,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}気付いたの　試されてる　意地悪な駆け引きで
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.49,0:25:35.99,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}已经注意到我在用坏心眼的谋略考验他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.26,0:25:39.05,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}後にはもう引けないから
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.26,0:25:39.05,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}已经不能退缩了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.08,0:25:41.88,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}仕掛けてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.08,0:25:41.88,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}让我给你设下圈套吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.94,0:25:49.06,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}さあ　掛かってみせて　戸惑ってみせて
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.94,0:25:49.06,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}来吧 掉进陷阱吧 不知所措吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.16,0:25:59.12,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}そして最後に伝えてみせて　好きだって
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.16,0:25:59.12,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}然后在最后说出那句喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.22,0:26:06.82,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君と私　どんな風に恋するの？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.22,0:26:06.81,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}你和我 将会怎样相恋呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.85,0:26:10.71,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}探る RELATION
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.85,0:26:10.71,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}去探索 RELATION
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.76,0:26:18.32,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}余裕なんてないよ　見つめられる度
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.76,0:26:18.32,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}每次被你注视 我一点都不从容哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.44,0:26:22.13,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}いつも震えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.44,0:26:22.13,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}我总是会颤抖着
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.24,0:26:29.11,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}素直じゃない私を連れ出して！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.24,0:26:29.11,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}请带走这样不坦率的我！
